{"id": "1443161172822982727", "channel_id": "1442825647138406480", "type": 0, "author_id": "1154601435141509192", "author_name": "jormiejormungandr", "author_bot": false, "content": "so many memories that are so difficult to compress in one collage! so i made two... i hope that's ok <:A_pinch:1432980538536493057> \n\nfirst collage:\n- the humble noob days, 7500 \"dream\" dive 😂 then there's the funni horla arith 📈 \n- the iconic thais login screen and chapter 7 shenanigans <:bow:1356053037159944473> \n- TULU!!! he had a tight grip on me since day 1, i love that man. the beautiful collage was made by anna <:T_sleep2:1356085993626665200> 💚 \n- aigis chapter. i remember that was the time i realized that \"happiness\" is only a concept in morimens, or rather a \"dream\"\n- 24 different personalities <:Clown:1400771541423226971> \n- \"it hurts doesn't it? sorry... i'll be more gentle\" out of context castor 😂 \n- POLLUX and his majestic back. i still remember how much some of us thirsted over that lol\n- and ofc, THE GTULU SILHOUTTE REVEAL. i haven't used any of my protos for his +12 <:pray:1356053116260454534> \n\nsecond collage:\n- daffodil's shop was the first bg i really really liked. took me a long time before i changed to other bg lol\n- the \"other bg\" is ofc N <:grin:1400771716665446471> 🛐 \n- and my current bg, the salvador one\n- then we have the tension........ and doom yuri 🛐", "timestamp": "2025-11-26T08:47:16.239000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "goodjob1", "emoji_id": "1356083729558274149", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "✨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1443161172105887744", "filename": "memory1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3282888, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1442825647138406480/1443161172105887744/memory1.png?ex=69ccdb94&is=69cb8a14&hm=a62414ab149a95daf6a9ac55d376cc25dcb19aa9cebcb020c2a327753154f786&"}, {"id": "1443161172856803338", "filename": "memory2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2672606, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1442825647138406480/1443161172856803338/memory2.png?ex=69ccdb94&is=69cb8a14&hm=b7c6a659fedbfb29cd2e01347a1dbd8a9e73108d107a27df061d7d824d5a7a61&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1442825647138406480", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🍰二周年有奖互动：晒出你的游生四宫格！Prize Event: Share Your Gaming Life in a Four-Grid Collage!", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1432652300182097985", "1432652180979978250", "1359482595934601266", "1359482693783388261"]}
