{"id": "1443303448966856846", "channel_id": "1442825647138406480", "type": 0, "author_id": "880443972055601173", "author_name": "gillamaru", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:realm_ultra:1437283545784651926>  A Year of Morimens <:realm_caro:1437283648134058004> \n\nIt’s been over a year since my partner first introduced me to Morimens, and it’s been an unforgettable adventure. What began as a casual game has transformed into something truly special.\n\nSo, here’s a little piece of our journey: a four-grid collage showing our five Steam accounts, each with a profile picture representing the Morimens account.\nEach account is a new path, a new realm to explore, and a new character to play.\n\nOn my main account I only play Ultra, while my partner's account is centered around Caro. Our favourite characters are Castor and GHelot, respectively.\nWe’ve also created additional accounts to explore the different realms and occasionally jump into Traphase for some PvP action. Recently, we even got some friends hooked on the game, and it’s been a blast sharing the experience. Morimens truly feels like a hidden gem in today’s gaming world.\n\nHere’s to another year! <:Cheerup:1400771555939844149>", "timestamp": "2025-11-26T18:12:37.515000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Showoff", "emoji_id": "1400771654199541850", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1443303448702484561", "filename": "Picture1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2851762, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1442825647138406480/1443303448702484561/Picture1.png?ex=69ccb755&is=69cb65d5&hm=2da13e9f5ba83bad90d962c5b58150f7aca9a3e2bd5a446d6d27b5b548a45bea&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1442825647138406480", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🍰二周年有奖互动：晒出你的游生四宫格！Prize Event: Share Your Gaming Life in a Four-Grid Collage!", "forum_channel_id": "13550850765005783